parameters:
This bed is so soft and comfortable. If I let my guard down, I
might end up falling asleep again...

\SE[49]And next to it... Luna's room... \SE[48]Just a 15-second
walk... Luna's room... \SM[nod]\SE[53]Paradise... was here...

\SE[85]Mom... Dad... There were many things... But now,
\SE[44]Laura is... \SM[nod]somehow, living happily...

\SE[102]Dinner... I have to go... \SM[tremble]\SE[38]I can't
move... My body...!

It's a dressing table. I haven't really done much makeup before,
but... should I give it a try too...?
It's a desk. Once I settle down, I'll gather various things...
It's a desk. Once I settle down, I'll gather various things...
This will be my diary. What to write... hehehe...

It's a wardrobe. It's still empty. If a ghost comes out, let's
hide here.
Here... What should I put here...? I'm thinking.
